input.content: How many solid cubes with dimensions 1.0 m (length) x 1.0 m (width) x 0.6 m (height) can fit in a box with dimensions 0.6 m (length) x 1.8 m (width) x 2.1 m (height)? You should only reply the answer. The answer should be in the form 'N cubes.', where N is the number of cubes that fit in the box.
